<h1 style="line-height: 1.25em"">Here is your daily reminder to check your temperature!</h1>

<p style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you for signing up to share you daily temperature! If you are interested in learning about this project and the data collected, please view our <%= link_to 'about page', about_url %>.</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px;">
  You can easily report your temperature for today using the links below:
</p>

<%= link_to 'Normal (Under 98.6F)', new_temperature_check_url({temperature: 'normal', age: @daily_temperature_check.age, loc_zip: @daily_temperature_check.loc_zip}), style: "background:#387bb2; color:#fff; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; padding:.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%; display: block; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;" %>

<%= link_to 'Not normal (click to add details)', new_temperature_check_url({temperature: 'fever', age: @daily_temperature_check.age, loc_zip: @daily_temperature_check.loc_zip}), style: "background:#b24738; color:#fff; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; padding:.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%; display: block; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;" %>
